title: Provide for display of Ten Commandments in public schools
Revise alternative energy project laws to require a bond prior to construction
Generally revise laws relating to wind generation facilities
Revise education laws to prohibit certain flags and banners in school and require phrase "In God we trust" displayed in each classroom of a public school
Generally revise laws related to sexual assault kits
Generally revise zoning laws to prohibit the construction of wind generation facilities.
